---

<style>
  .heading-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  h1 {
    text-align: center;
  }

  hr {
    background: var(--mid-grey);
    width: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .sub-heading {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .final-wrapper {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
</style>
<Layout
  title="Mortgages, Home Loans & Refinancing"
  image=""
  description="Discover your path to homeownership with Kasey Home Loans. Our expert mortgage professionals provide tailored solutions to secure your dream home. Explore competitive rates, personalized guidance, and hassle-free financing options today."
>
  <div class="heading-wrapper compressed container">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <hr />
    <div class="sub-heading center">High level professionals for superior home buying experience.</div>
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <div class="about">
      <p>
        Welcome to Kasey Home Loans, where transparency, accuracy, knowledge, and expertise converge to empower your
        journey towards homeownership. Founded by Ramsin Kuryakoos and Aaron Conway, Kasey Home Loans is built upon the
        belief that securing a home loan should be a seamless and consistent experience.
      </p>

      <h3>Transparency</h3>
      <p>
        At Kasey Home Loans, we prioritize transparency above all else. We've answered questions most lenders don't want
        to with our <a href="/faq">frequently asked questions</a> and our <a href="/learn">Learning Center</a> provides insights
        you can't get anywher else. We understand that navigating the complexities of the mortgage process can be daunting,
        which is why we strive to provide clear and concise information every step of the way. Whether you're a first-time
        homebuyer or a seasoned investor, <b
          >you can trust us to keep you informed and educated throughout the entire process.</b
        >
        <h3>Accuracy</h3>
        <p>
          <b>We know it's incredibly difficult to get accurate information online</b>. Our team of experts is dedicated
          to ensuring that every detail is meticulously reviewed and verified, giving you the confidence to make
          informed decisions about your financial future.
        </p>

        <h3>Knowledge</h3>
        <p>
          Our commitment to high-level knowledge is what sets us apart as a company. We invest heavily and develop our
          own tools that allow us to providing accurate quotes and maintain our guideline knowledge. Not only do we have
          years of experience in the mortgage industry, <b
            >we activley study the guidelines to navigate even the most complex financial situations</b
          >. We stay ahead of the curve, continuously expanding our knowledge and adapting to changes in the market to
          better serve you.
        </p>

        <h3>Speed</h3>
        <p>
          Speed isn't just important for convenience. Being able to deliver answers on a weekend in a short period of
          time can be the difference in securing a home. <b>We prioritize efficiency without compromising on quality.</b
          > Our streamlined processes and cutting-edge technology enable us to expedite the loan approval process without
          missing important steps, getting you one step closer to achieving your homeownership goals.
        </p>

        <SimpleCTA />
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="final-wrapper">
    <div class="sub-heading center">We look forward to working with you.</div>
  </div>
</Layout>
